clk: tegra: Fix refcount leak in tegra114_clock_init

This is an automated ID intended to aid in discovery of potential security vulnerabilities. The actual impact and attack plausibility have not yet been proven.
This ID is fixed in Linux Kernel version v4.19.262 by commit 8cc87a9c142ae0e276a3ff9ce50f78a1668da36f, it was introduced in version v3.10 by commit 2cb5efefd6f7d3e7df9a7430b910a80515821256. For more details please see the references link.
